---
title: Rosemary Beef Flatbread with Caramelized Onion & Broccoli
description: Beef, rosemary, and garlic are a match made in flavor heaven. Served atop crispy flatbread whit caramelized onions, gooey mozzarella, and tender broccoli, we guarantee you won't have any leftovers!
